flow_state|social_exchange_deep_focus_creative_movement_physical_rhythm|narrowing_1|1|Staying in the exchange too long|You may keep explaining, responding, or discussing after the work would benefit from quiet attention and a clearer choice.|social_exchange|active|flow_state::social_exchange_deep_focus_creative_movement_physical_rhythm::narrowing_1
flow_state|social_exchange_deep_focus_creative_movement_physical_rhythm|narrowing_2|2|Leaving the insight undeveloped|A useful point may appear in conversation, but lose strength if it does not get focused time afterwards.|deep_focus|active|flow_state::social_exchange_deep_focus_creative_movement_physical_rhythm::narrowing_2
flow_state|social_exchange_deep_focus_creative_movement_physical_rhythm|narrowing_3|3|Missing the reset signal|You may stay mentally available to other people after your attention, body, or energy already needs a pause.|physical_rhythm|active|flow_state::social_exchange_deep_focus_creative_movement_physical_rhythm::narrowing_3
13_Application
domain_key|pattern_key|application_area|guidance_type|priority|guidance_text|linked_signal_key|status|lookup_key
flow_state|social_exchange_deep_focus_creative_movement_physical_rhythm|use_this_when|guidance|1|Use this pattern when the work needs live sense-making, feedback, teaching, facilitation, client discussion, or shared problem-solving. Let the exchange open the work before trying to finalise it alone.|social_exchange|active|flow_state::social_exchange_deep_focus_creative_movement_physical_rhythm::use_this_when
flow_state|social_exchange_deep_focus_creative_movement_physical_rhythm|watch_for|guidance|2|Watch for the moment when more talking stops improving the work. That is often the point to pause, focus, write down the useful insight, or choose the next decision.|deep_focus|active|flow_state::social_exchange_deep_focus_creative_movement_physical_rhythm::watch_for
flow_state|social_exchange_deep_focus_creative_movement_physical_rhythm|develop_by|guidance|3|Develop by building a reset after important exchanges. Step away, move, change setting, or take a short pause before responding to the next thing.|physical_rhythm|active|flow_state::social_exchange_deep_focus_creative_movement_physical_rhythm::develop_by
14_Closing_Integration
domain_key|pattern_key|score_shape|closing_summary|core_gift|core_trap|development_edge|memorable_line|status|lookup_key
flow_state|social_exchange_deep_focus_creative_movement_physical_rhythm|concentrated|This result points to a flow style built around exchange, then focus. You are likely to do your best work when conversation, feedback, or shared problem-solving helps attention start, then focus, new angles, and reset help the work become clear and useful.|Your gift is the ability to create clarity, energy, and momentum through live exchange with other people.|The trap is staying in the exchange after the work needs quiet focus, recovery, or a clear decision.|The useful edge is to step back at the right time so the exchange can turn into focused clarity.|Talk it through. Then step back and make the useful part stronger.|active|flow_state::social_exchange_deep_focus_creative_movement_physical_rhythm::concentrated
